data.description: Seize this outstanding investment opportunity at 350 Quail Meadow Rd, Seadrift, TX 77983! This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom property offers the ideal canvas for a savvy investor. With central air-heat, new windows, and a recently replaced roof in 2017, the foundation is solid. Plus, it comes with valuable features like a new front workshop-shed with electricity, a water well house, and an above-ground pool. The 14-ft automatic gate, 2-car garage, and 2-car carport provide ample parking and security. While there's no basement, the potential for a profitable return on investment is undeniable. Don't let this opportunity slip away – it's time to make your mark in the real estate mark
